vote.title: Authorize the City Manager to provide the Notice of Intent to establish a Quiet Zone along the Union Pacific Railroad corridor encompassing the railroad crossings at Prairie Creek Road and Sam Houston Road as provided for in the Federal Railroad Administration’s Final Train Horn Rule - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
